OL,3,CPolice boss apologises to families of
OL,4,Cattack victims for 'lack of empathy'
OL,6,FA senior police officer from
OL,7,FNottinghamshire Police has apologised
OL,8,Fto the families of those who were
OL,9,Fkilled in the Nottingham attacks.
OL,11,FThe official inquiry into the attacks,
OL,12,Fwhere three people were killed in June
OL,13,F2023, is underway in central London
OL,14,Fand started a month ago.
OL,16,FRob Griffin, who was the Assistant
OL,17,FChief Constable at the time of the
OL,18,Fattacks in June 2023 was asked about a
OL,19,Fstatement released at the time which
OL,20,Fsaid that police could not have
OL,21,Fstopped what happened.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/8
