CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1774289155
OL,3,CPolice boss apologises to families of
OL,4,Cattack victims for 'lack of empathy'
OL,6,FFormer mechanical engineering student
OL,7,FValdo Calocane fatally stabbed
OL,8,FUniversity of Nottingham
OL,9,Fundergraduates Barnaby Webber and
OL,10,FGrace O'Malley-Kumar, both 19, and
OL,11,Fgrandfather Ian Coates, 65, and
OL,12,Fattempted to kill three more people in
OL,13,Fthe early hours of June 13.
OL,15,FIn that statement, Mr Griffin said:
OL,16,F"I'm really confident that everything
OL,17,Fthat we did was thorough and
OL,18,Fprofessional.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1774289155
OL,3,CPolice boss apologises to families of
OL,4,Cattack victims for 'lack of empathy'
OL,6,F"I wouldn't have looked to have
OL,7,Fchanged anything, and tragically, we
OL,8,Fcouldn't have stopped any of what
OL,9,Fhappened."
OL,11,FMr Griffin said "When I reflect on it
OL,12,Fnow, I can see the impact those words
OL,13,Fare likely to have on the bereaved
OL,14,Ffamilies and survivors. They are words
OL,15,FI regret, yes.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@JO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1774289155
OL,3,CPolice boss apologises to families of
OL,4,Cattack victims for 'lack of empathy'
OL,6,F"I want to say again I'm so, so sorry
OL,7,Fabout that. There are many parts of
OL,8,Fthose statements that I believe are
OL,9,Ftrue ` it was the tone and the choice
OL,10,Fof the words and the lack of empathy
OL,11,Fthat is what I really reflect on, and
OL,12,FI apologise for that again."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@\O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1774289155
OL,3,CPolice boss apologises to families of
OL,4,Cattack victims for 'lack of empathy'
OL,6,FChairwoman Deborah Taylor heard that
OL,7,Fwhen Calocane was sentenced in January
OL,8,F2024 to a hospital order after
OL,9,Fpleading guilty to three counts of
OL,10,Fmanslaughter on the grounds of
OL,11,Fdiminished responsibility and three
OL,12,Fcounts of attempted murder, the
OL,13,Fbereaved families were not liaised
OL,14,Fwith about police press statements.
OL,16,FMr Griffin said of this: "I can see,
OL,17,Fand saw on the day of sentence, the
OL,18,Fhurt that I had caused which was quite
OL,19,Fthe opposite of my intention.
OL,26,@xD@ZOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1774289155
OL,3,CPolice boss apologises to families of
OL,4,Cattack victims for 'lack of empathy'
OL,6,F"I have never had the opportunity to
OL,7,Fsay it to the families, that I'm so,
OL,8,Fso sorry about that."
OL,10,FJulian Blake, counsel to the inquiry
OL,11,Fasked Mr Griffin when it was "realised
OL,12,Fthat there was a serious systemic
OL,13,Foperational failures" and he replied
OL,14,F"almost immediately" but that the
OL,15,Ffamilies were never informed.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@UO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1774289155
OL,3,CPolice boss apologises to families of
OL,4,Cattack victims for 'lack of empathy'
OL,6,FHe was also questioned about the
OL,7,Fpolice search for Calocane, "My
OL,8,Fevidence is the search activity should
OL,9,Fof been more co-ordinated. It was not
OL,10,Fas good and as efficient as it should
OL,11,Fof been."
OL,13,FThe officer said Calocane ended up
OL,14,Falmost a mile and a half away by
OL,15,F4.41am, adding: "Reflecting on all of
OL,16,Fthat, I can understand now why we
OL,17,Fdidn't find him."
OL,19,FThe inquiry heard that information was
OL,20,Fknown about Mr Webber's identity from
OL,21,Faround 4.20am.
OL,26,@wD@QOUyD@QO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
