PN,37108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1774289155
OL,3,CPolice boss apologises to families of
OL,4,Cattack victims for 'lack of empathy'
OL,6,FMr Griffin said he would prefer if the
OL,7,Fbereaved families had been told about
OL,8,Fthe attacks earlier.
OL,10,FHe said: "The parents of Barney and
OL,11,FGrace should have been told just as
OL,12,Fsoon as was humanly possible. And I
OL,13,Fcompletely understand the impact of
OL,14,Fthem not having been."
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
